<div id="p2-w56" class="wd">
<div class="wk-banner">
  <div class="wk-title">Weeks 5–6 (June Wk3–4) — Final Build <span class="change-tag">↑ CHANGE</span></div>
  <div class="wk-note">Run both weeks · Golf is 4 rounds/wk · Last heavy volume before peak golf</div>
  <div class="wk-loads">Snatch ~87% feel → 3×2 @ 78% (168) · C&amp;J ~87% feel → 3×2 @ 78% (222) · Squat 5×4 @ 76% (315) · Bench ~87% feel → 4×3 @ 80% (256) · TBD 4×4 @ 72% (328)</div>
</div>
