<div class="al al-fire"><h4>Golf Is Now 4 Rounds/Week — Adjust Scheduling</h4><ul>
  <li>Never schedule Session A or C (heavy lower/Oly) the day before or after 18 holes</li>
  <li>Session B (bench) and Session D (hypertrophy) can go adjacent to golf — zero spinal load</li>
  <li>If shift pattern means you can only fit 3 gym sessions this week: drop Session D, keep A, B, and C</li>
</ul></div>
