<!-- ██ BLOCK 3 ██ -->
<div id="p3" class="pd">
<div class="pi"><strong>Block 3 — Peak Golf · July–August · 9 Weeks</strong><br>
Golf is 5 rounds/wk. This is the block that broke your back last year. Fix: 3 gym sessions/wk. Full squat Oly stays — heavy singles are in — but back-offs drop from 3 to 2. Bench does NOT reduce. Hypertrophy session stays. Grouped into 3-week micro-blocks (same % for 3 weeks, then a small jump).</div>
<div class="wtabs">
  <button class="wt on" onclick="sW('p3','w13',this)">Wks 1–3 (Early Jul)</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p3','w46',this)">Wks 4–6 (Late Jul)</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p3','w79',this)">Wks 7–9 (August)</button>
</div>
<div class="al al-blu" style="margin-bottom:14px;"><h4>Block 3 Weekly Structure — Every Week</h4><ul>
  <li><strong>Session A (2 days post-shift, NOT adjacent to golf):</strong> Full Oly + Squat + Trap Bar DL. Never skip this one.</li>
  <li><strong>Session B (not adjacent to heavy lower body day):</strong> Bench heavy + Spoto + Tricep. Can be closer to golf — no spinal load.</li>
  <li><strong>Station workout (shift):</strong> Upper + core + Zone 2. Unchanged.</li>
  <li><strong>Session C (off day — can be day after golf if SIJ clear):</strong> Hypertrophy + Beach + lighter trap bar.</li>
  <li><strong>Cardio 2×/wk:</strong> Easy 20–25 min run or bike only. Golf walking is your Zone 2 base.</li>
</ul></div>

<div id="p3-w13" class="wd on">
<div class="wk-banner">
