  <div class="wk-note">Run 3 consecutive weeks at these numbers</div>
  <div class="wk-loads">Snatch ~85% feel → 2×2 @ 78% (168) · C&amp;J ~85% feel → 2×2 @ 78% (222) · Squat 4×3 @ 80% (332) · Bench ~86% feel → 4×3 @ 80% (256) · TBD A: 3×4 @ 74% (337) · TBD C: 3×6 @ 65% (296)</div>
</div>
