<div class="al al-red"><h4>August Warning System</h4><ul>
  <li>SIJ pain 2–3/10: switch Oly to hang that week only. Keep everything else. Tell physio next session.</li>
  <li>SIJ pain 3–4/10: cap golf at 2 rounds. Drop all DL. Squats OK if pain-free in warmup. Ice 15 min × 3/day.</li>
  <li>Pain radiating into glute or leg: stop all loading. Disc or nerve, not SIJ. Physio same week.</li>
  <li>If you miss a week: come back at Wks 4–6 numbers, not where you left off.</li>
</ul></div>
