<!-- ██ BLOCK 4 ██ -->
<div id="p4" class="pd">
<div class="pi"><strong>Block 4 — Golf Wind-Down + Push · September · 4 Weeks</strong><br>
Golf drops to 4 rounds/wk. Gym rebuilds to 4 proper sessions. Oly loads push to real heavy territory. Back-off sets return to 3. Bench inches toward true max. Sprints/plyo every 10–14 days. Conventional DL returns Week 4 only if SIJ pain-free for 2+ consecutive weeks. Each week written individually.</div>
<div class="wtabs">
  <button class="wt on" onclick="sW('p4','w1',this)">Week 1</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p4','w2',this)">Week 2</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p4','w3',this)">Week 3</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p4','w4',this)">Week 4</button>
</div>
<div class="al al-blu" style="margin-bottom:14px;"><h4>Block 4 Weekly Structure</h4><ul>
  <li><strong>Session A (2 days post-shift):</strong> Snatch + Squat — loads climbing</li>
  <li><strong>Session B (next off day):</strong> Bench heavy + floor press + upper</li>
  <li><strong>Session C (off day):</strong> C&amp;J + DL + Pull</li>
  <li><strong>Session D (off day):</strong> Hypertrophy + Arms. Sprint/plyo before session every 10–14 days if SIJ clear.</li>
  <li><strong>Station workout (shift):</strong> Same as always</li>
  <li><strong>Cardio 2×/wk:</strong> 30–35 min Zone 2. One session can be replaced by sprint session.</li>
</ul></div>

