<div class="al al-fire"><h4>Conventional DL Returns — Do It Right</h4><ul>
  <li>Only if SIJ has been completely pain-free for 2+ weeks. If not: stay on trap bar one more week.</li>
  <li>Start at 80% (348 lb) — not where you left off in April. Build in carefully.</li>
  <li>If any SIJ response to conventional DL: back to trap bar for remainder of Block 4. Conv DL fully available in Block 5.</li>
</ul></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ██ BLOCK 5 ██ -->
<div id="p5" class="pd">
<div class="pi"><strong>Block 5 — Strength Rebuild · October · 4 Weeks</strong><br>
Golf drops to 3 rounds/wk then ends. 5 gym sessions/wk. Conv. DL fully integrated. Oly lifts approach true max territory. Bench closes in on new 1RM. By end of Week 4 you're ready for November max attempts.</div>
<div class="wtabs">
  <button class="wt on" onclick="sW('p5','w1',this)">Week 1</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p5','w2',this)">Week 2</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p5','w3',this)">Week 3</button>
  <button class="wt" onclick="sW('p5','w4',this)">Week 4</button>
</div>
<div class="al al-blu" style="margin-bottom:14px;"><h4>Block 5 — 5 Session Weekly Structure</h4><ul>
  <li><strong>Session A:</strong> Snatch + Back Squat + Front Squat</li>
  <li><strong>Session B:</strong> Bench + Floor Press + Spoto Press + Tricep</li>
  <li><strong>Session C:</strong> C&amp;J + Conventional DL + Pull</li>
  <li><strong>Session D:</strong> Upper volume — OHP, weighted pull-ups, arms, shoulders</li>
  <li><strong>Session E:</strong> Lower accessory — front squat, RDL, legs, carries</li>
  <li><strong>Cardio 2×/wk:</strong> 28–30 min Zone 2 run or bike</li>
</ul></div>

